#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:105
msgid ""
"These actions are all available from the \\I{Game menu}\\q{Game} menu and "
"via \\I{keys}keyboard shortcuts, in addition to any game-specific actions."
msgstr ""
"这些操作都可以从 \\I{Game menu}\\q{Game} 菜单和通过 "
"\\I{keys}键盘快捷键获得，除了任何特定于游戏的操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:109
msgid ""
"(On \\i{Mac OS X}, to conform with local user interface standards, these "
"actions are situated on the \\I{File menu}\\q{File} and \\I{Edit "
"menu}\\q{Edit} menus instead.)"
msgstr ""
"（在 \\i{Mac OS X} 上，为了符合本地用户界面标准，这些操作"
"位于 \\I{File menu}\\q{File} 和 \\I{Edit menu}\\q{Edit} 菜单上。）"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:111
msgid "\\ii\\e{New game} (\\q{N}, Ctrl+\\q{N})"
msgstr "\\ii\\e{新游戏}（\\q{N}，Ctrl+\\q{N}）"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:113
msgid "Starts a new game, with a random initial state."
msgstr "开始一个新游戏，具有随机的初始状态。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:115
msgid "\\ii\\e{Restart game}"
msgstr "\\ii\\e{重新开始游戏}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:117
msgid "Resets the current game to its initial state. (This can be undone.)"
msgstr "将当前游戏重置为其初始状态。（这可以撤销。）"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:119
msgid "\\ii\\e{Load}"
msgstr "\\ii\\e{加载}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:121
msgid "Loads a saved game from a file on disk."
msgstr "从磁盘上的文件加载已保存的游戏。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:123
msgid "\\ii\\e{Save}"
msgstr "\\ii\\e{保存}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:125
msgid "Saves the current state of your game to a file on disk."
msgstr "将您游戏的当前状态保存到磁盘上的文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:133
msgid ""
"The Load and Save operations preserve your entire game history (so you can "
"save, reload, and still Undo and Redo things you had done before saving)."
msgstr ""
"加载和保存操作保留您的整个游戏历史记录（因此您可以保存、重新加载，"
"并仍然撤销和重做您在保存之前所做的操作）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:135
msgid "\\I{printing, on Windows}\\e{Print}"
msgstr "\\I{打印，在 Windows 上}\\e{打印}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:142
msgid ""
"Where supported (currently only on Windows), brings up a dialog allowing you "
"to print an arbitrary number of puzzles randomly generated from the current "
"parameters, optionally including the current puzzle. (Only for puzzles which "
"make sense to print, of course \\dash it's hard to think of a sensible "
"printable representation of Fifteen!)"
msgstr ""
"在支持的地方（目前仅在 Windows 上），会弹出一个对话框，允许您"
"打印从当前参数随机生成的任意数量的谜题，可选地包括当前谜题。"
"（当然，仅适用于值得打印的谜题 \\dash 很难想到一个可打印的 Fifteen 的合理表示！）"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:144
msgid "\\ii\\e{Undo} (\\q{U}, Ctrl+\\q{Z}, Ctrl+\\q{_}, \\q{*})"
msgstr "\\ii\\e{撤销}（\\q{U}，Ctrl+\\q{Z}，Ctrl+\\q{_}，\\q{*}）"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:147
msgid ""
"Undoes a single move. (You can undo moves back to the start of the session.)"
msgstr ""
"撤销单个操作。（您可以撤销操作直到会话开始。）"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:149
msgid "\\ii\\e{Redo} (\\q{R}, Ctrl+\\q{R}, \\q{#})"
msgstr "\\ii\\e{重做}（\\q{R}，Ctrl+\\q{R}，\\q{#}）"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:151
msgid "Redoes a previously undone move."
msgstr "重做之前撤销的操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:153
msgid "\\ii\\e{Copy}"
msgstr "\\ii\\e{复制}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:158
msgid ""
"Copies the current state of your game to the clipboard in text format, so "
"that you can paste it into (say) an e-mail client or a web message board if "
"you're discussing the game with someone else. (Not all games support this "
"feature.)"
msgstr ""
"将您游戏的当前状态以文本格式复制到剪贴板，以便您可以将其"
"粘贴到（比如说）电子邮件客户端或网络留言板，如果您正在与别人讨论游戏的话。"
"（并非所有游戏都支持此功能。）"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:160
msgid "\\ii\\e{Solve}"
msgstr "\\ii\\e{求解}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:170
msgid ""
"Transforms the puzzle instantly into its solved state. For some games (Cube) "
"this feature is not supported at all because it is of no particular use. For "
"other games (such as Pattern), the solved state can be used to give you "
"information, if you can't see how a solution can exist at all or you want to "
"know where you made a mistake. For still other games (such as Sixteen), "
"automatic solution tells you nothing about how to \\e{get} to the solution, "
"but it does provide a useful way to get there quickly so that you can "
"experiment with set-piece moves and transformations."
msgstr ""
"立即将谜题转换为其已解决状态。对于某些游戏（Cube），此功能"
"根本不受支持，因为它没有特别的用途。对于其他游戏（如 Pattern），"
"如果根本看不出如何存在解决方案，或者您想知道在哪里犯了错误，"
"已解决状态可以为您提供信息。对于还有其他游戏（如 Sixteen），"
"自动解决方案不会告诉您如何 \\e{到达}解决方案，但它确实提供了一种"
"快速到达那里以便您可以尝试固定棋步和转换的有用方法。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:172
msgid "\\I{types}Type"
msgstr "\\I{types}类型"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:174
msgid "\\ii\\e{Type} (\\q{T})"
msgstr "\\ii\\e{类型}（\\q{T}）"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:176
msgid ""
"Pops up a dialog box allowing you to change the parameters with which the "
"game is generated (for example the grid size, or the difficulty level).  The "
"\\e{Game ID} and \\e{Seed} values are also displayed in this dialog, so "
"you can copy them if you want to send a game to someone else."
msgstr ""
"弹出一个对话框，允许您更改生成游戏的参数（例如网格大小或难度级别）。"
"\\e{游戏 ID} 和 \\e{种子} 值也显示在此对话框中，因此如果您想将"
"游戏发送给其他人，可以复制它们。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:185
msgid ""
"Some games allow you to change the game parameters using the keyboard, via "
"the \\q{Type} menu item and a series of dialog boxes."
msgstr ""
"某些游戏允许您使用键盘通过 \\q{类型} 菜单项和一系列对话框"
"更改游戏参数。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:187
msgid "In these cases, there is also a \\q{Custom} menu item."
msgstr "在这些情况下，还有一个 \\q{自定义} 菜单项。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:189
msgid ""
"This brings up a dialog box containing a text entry field in which you can type "
"in game parameters exactly as you would type them on the command line, or paste in "
"a \\e{Game ID} or \\e{Seed} value copied from another game."
msgstr ""
"这将弹出一个对话框，其中包含一个文本输入字段，您可以在其中输入游戏参数，"
"就像您在命令行上输入它们一样，或者粘贴从另一个游戏复制的 "
"\\e{游戏 ID} 或 \\e{种子} 值。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:192
msgid ""
"See the \\c{manual page} for details of the parameters for each game, "
"and the \\c{game IDs} section for more detail about the precise format "
"and purpose of game IDs."
msgstr ""
"有关每个游戏的参数详细信息，请参阅 \\c{手册页}，有关游戏 ID 的"
"精确格式和目的的更多详细信息，请参阅 \\c{游戏 ID} 部分。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:200
msgid "Game IDs"
msgstr "游戏 ID"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:202
msgid ""
"The \\e{Type} dialog box for each game displays a text string called the "
"\\e{Game ID}. This text string uniquely identifies a particular game "
"instance; you can use it to communicate a particular puzzle to a friend."
msgstr ""
"每个游戏的 \\e{类型} 对话框显示一个称为 \\e{游戏 ID} 的文本字符串。"
"此文本字符串唯一标识特定的游戏实例；您可以使用它向朋友传达特定的谜题。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:207
msgid ""
"A game ID is generated from the parameters of the game (size, shape, "
"difficulty, and so on)."
msgstr ""
"游戏 ID 是从游戏的参数（大小、形状、难度等）生成的。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:209
msgid ""
"Conversely, given a Game ID, the game will generate the exact puzzle "
"that was originally created using it."
msgstr ""
"相反，给定游戏 ID，游戏将生成最初使用它创建的确切谜题。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:211
msgid ""
"So you can use this feature to send a particular puzzle to a friend, or "
"record a particularly good one and come back to it later.  It also enables you "
"to report puzzles that are unsolvable or otherwise buggy."
msgstr ""
"因此，您可以使用此功能将特定的谜题发送给朋友，或者记录一个特别好"
"的谜题并在以后返回。它还使您能够报告不可解决或有其他错误的谜题。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:218
msgid ""
"(Note: the Game ID is not guaranteed to be the same across different "
"versions of the game. If you're passing puzzle specifications between people "
"who have different versions of the software, you should also exchange a \\e{Seed} "
"value, which is more stable.)"
msgstr ""
"（注意：游戏 ID 不保证在游戏的不同版本中相同。如果您在拥有不同"
"软件版本的人员之间传递谜题规范，您还应该交换一个 \\e{种子} 值，"
"该值更稳定。）"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:223
msgid "Seeds"
msgstr "种子"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:225
msgid ""
"The \\e{Type} dialog box for each game also displays a text string called the "
"\\e{Seed}.  This is a random number generated when the game is created."
msgstr ""
"每个游戏的 \\e{类型} 对话框还显示一个称为 \\e{种子} 的文本字符串。"
"这是创建游戏时生成的随机数。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:228
msgid ""
"The seed value can be used to reproduce exactly the same set of puzzles, "
"perhaps by different people at different times."
msgstr ""
"种子值可用于重现完全相同的谜题集，可能由不同人在不同时间重现。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:231
msgid ""
"If you type a seed value into the \\e{Custom} game parameter dialog, the "
"game will generate exactly the same puzzles it would have generated if it had "
"created that seed value itself at random."
msgstr ""
"如果您在 \\e{自定义} 游戏参数对话框中输入种子值，游戏将生成完全相同的"
"谜题，就像它自己随机创建该种子值一样。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:236
msgid ""
"Game IDs include a seed value within them. However, the seed value is "
"more stable across different versions of the game, and it is the seed that "
"should be used if you want to communicate a puzzle set to someone else."
msgstr ""
"游戏 ID 在其中包含一个种子值。但是，种子值在游戏的不同版本中更稳定，"
"如果您想向其他人传达谜题集，应该使用的是种子。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:244
msgid "The \\e{Type} menu also contains game-specific configuration options."
msgstr "\\e{类型} 菜单还包含特定于游戏的配置选项。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:246
msgid ""
"For example, \\i{Black Box} has an option to control whether the "
"solution to the puzzle is revealed when it is finished, and whether to "
"display a count of how many balls have been correctly or incorrectly placed."
msgstr ""
"例如，\\i{Black Box} 有一个选项可以控制在谜题完成时是否揭示解决方案，"
"以及是否显示正确或错误放置的球数的计数。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:253
msgid ""
"These options are described in the chapter for each individual game, under the "
"heading \\i{Configuration options} or similar."
msgstr ""
"这些选项在各个游戏的章节中描述，位于标题 \\i{配置选项} 或类似标题下。"

#. type: h3
#: puzzles.but:258
msgid "Common actions"
msgstr "常见操作"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:260
msgid ""
"These actions are available in all of the games. They are all available "
"from the \\I{Game menu}\\q{Game} menu."
msgstr ""
"这些操作在所有游戏中都可用。它们都可以从 "
"\\I{Game menu}\\q{Game} 菜单获得。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:265
msgid "\\I{newgame,keys}\\c{New game}"
msgstr "\\I{newgame,keys}\\c{新游戏}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:267
msgid ""
"Starts a new game. By default, the new game will have random parameters. "
"You can also start a new game by pressing one of the numbers on the \\e{Type} "
"menu, which will generate a game of that difficulty. You can also start a "
"game from a Game ID or Seed copied from elsewhere, via the \\e{Custom} "
"option."
msgstr ""
"开始一个新游戏。默认情况下，新游戏将具有随机参数。您还可以通过按"
"\\e{类型} 菜单上的数字之一开始一个新游戏，这将生成该难度的游戏。"
"您还可以通过 \\e{自定义} 选项从别处复制的游戏 ID 或种子开始游戏。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:283
msgid "\\I{restartgame,keys}\\c{Restart game}"
msgstr "\\I{restartgame,keys}\\c{重新开始游戏}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:285
msgid "Resets the current puzzle to its initial state."
msgstr "将当前谜题重置为其初始状态。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:287
msgid "\\I{specific}\\i{Black Box}: \\c{Verify guesses}"
msgstr "\\I{specific}\\i{Black Box}：\\c{验证猜测}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:289
msgid "Check whether the marked balls are correctly placed."
msgstr "检查标记的球是否正确放置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:291
msgid "\\I{loadgame,keys}\\c{Load}"
msgstr "\\I{loadgame,keys}\\c{加载}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:293
msgid "Loads a saved game from a file."
msgstr "从文件加载已保存的游戏。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:295
msgid "\\I{savegame,keys}\\c{Save}"
msgstr "\\I{savegame,keys}\\c{保存}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:297
msgid "Saves the current game to a file."
msgstr "将当前游戏保存到文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:299
msgid "\\I{undo,keys}\\c{Undo}"
msgstr "\\I{undo,keys}\\c{撤销}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:301
msgid "Undoes a single move."
msgstr "撤销单个操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:303
msgid "\\I{redo,keys}\\c{Redo}"
msgstr "\\I{redo,keys}\\c{重做}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:305
msgid "Redoes a previously undone move."
msgstr "重做之前撤销的操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:307
msgid "\\I{type,keys}\\c{Type}"
msgstr "\\I{type,keys}\\c{类型}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:309
msgid ""
"Brings up the game configuration dialog, allowing you to change the "
"difficulty or the game size, among other things."
msgstr ""
"弹出游戏配置对话框，允许您更改难度或游戏大小等。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:314
msgid "\\I{solve,keys}\\c{Solve}"
msgstr "\\I{solve,keys}\\c{求解}"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:316
msgid ""
"Solves the current puzzle immediately, where possible. Some games (e.g. "
"Fifteen) are effectively not solvable, so this menu item will be disabled."
msgstr ""
"立即解决当前谜题（可能的话）。某些游戏（如 Fifteen）实际上不可解决，"
"因此此菜单项将被禁用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:320
msgid "Licence"
msgstr "许可"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:322
msgid ""
"The puzzles in this collection were mostly originally written by Simon Tatham.  "
"Some puzzles (e.g. \\i{Mines}) have been written by other people.  A "
"few puzzles contain code from other sources, including some code from \\i{Richard "
"T. Guy} and the GNU documentation system."
msgstr ""
"此合集中的谜题大多最初由 Simon Tatham 编写。一些谜题（如 "
"\\i{Mines}）由其他人编写。少数谜题包含来自其他来源的代码，"
"包括来自 \\i{Richard T. Guy} 和 GNU 文档系统的一些代码。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:331
msgid ""
"In some cases, those authors have requested credit and a copyright notice, "
"which is reproduced in the individual game descriptions below."
msgstr ""
"在某些情况下，这些作者要求署名和版权声明，这些在下面的各个游戏描述中转载。"

#. type: Plain text
#: puzzles.but:334
msgid ""
"I have therefore given this collection a unified licence. The MIT licence is a "
"permissive non-copyleft free software licence which permits people to reuse "
"the code for any purpose.  The full text of the licence is reproduced "
"below."
msgstr ""
"因此，我为这个合集提供了一个统一的许可。MIT 许可证是一个宽松的"
"非 copyleft 自由软件许可，允许人们将代码用于任何目的。"
"许可的全文转载如下。"

